__e: For your good service and ingenuity in uniting the Houses of Lannister and Tyrell, I declare that you shall be granted the castle of Harrenhal with all its attendant lands and incomes to be held by your sons and grandsons from this day until the end of time.
Riverrun cannot stand against the Lannisters and the Freys.
After the Lannisters and the Starks, the Tyrells command the largest host.
